### Register our first trader
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "trader_alex",
  "email": "alex@tradesim.com"
}

### Place a BUY Order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "57df4250-47bb-46e7-b9e7-9fd52b016f88",
  "ticker": "AAPL",
  "side": "BUY",
  "price": 150.00,
  "quantity": 10
}